{"tid":2007960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄羅斯持續日增逾萬個案 南韓再現本土感染","createTime":"2020-05-08T16:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T16:35:08.000Z","uid":166360,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"62daacc47e52efc9def580b246a6751f4830ca91","tid":2007960,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯持續日增逾萬個案 南韓再現本土感染<br />\n2020-05-08 HKT 22:01<br />\n<br />\n美國的新型冠狀病毒感染個案增至超過120萬宗，超過7萬人死亡，總統特朗普一名隨從亦確診。特朗普說自己與副總統彭斯已接受病毒測試，兩人結果都是陰性。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲方面，俄羅斯連續第六天新增超過1萬宗病例，超過一半個案來自首都莫斯科。多國在疫情下都不再舉行大型活動，紀念二次大戰「歐戰勝利日」75周年。<br />\n<br />\n疫情近日轉趨穩定的南韓，再次爆發集體社區感染，新增13宗確診病例都與首爾市夜店群組有關，當局要求全國夜店今晚開始暫停營業一個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1525087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1525087&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=67a5e194\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1525087&h=3393ca17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1525087</a>"},{"pid":"85aea3d500723f767668a4da78c2331a40b58cac","tid":2007960,"uid":223741,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"普京唔知點諗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfc1910282c971c1bb94f4d7cfa91b91290b1e8","tid":2007960,"uid":184488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85aea3d500723f767668a4da78c2331a40b58cac","tid":2007960,"uid":223741,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"普京唔知點諗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"陰公豬，5/9大閱兵都搞唔成，冇得紀念衛國戰爭烈士+晒馬"},{"pid":"3ec86f08a